summary: An FBI email from December 2019 regarding a tip received by a local crime stoppers line about a teenager whose name appeared on a flight log for one of Jeffrey Epstein's planes, traveling from SAF to ZOR, with a specific pilot listed. The sender is seeking FBI assistance to verify information and help the local Sheriff's office.

events.description: A local crime stoppers line received a tip that a teenager's name was listed on a flight log for one of Jeffrey Epstein's planes flying from SAF to ZOR.

keyFacts: A tip was received by a local crime stoppers line regarding a teenager on an Epstein flight log.
The flight was on one of Jeffrey Epstein's planes from SAF to ZOR.
A specific pilot was listed on the flight log, but the name is redacted in the document.
The FBI was contacted to assist in verifying the information and helping the local Sheriff's office.
The document indicates ongoing investigative interest in Epstein's flight logs as of late 2019.
